These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, dahlia, bellflower
House: art-deco, cottage, farmhouse, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
4 different pets are kept: snake, bird, rat, fish
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
 3. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 6. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 8. the palace house is between the owner of the bird and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the owner of the fish is the farmhouse house##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
12. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
13. the farmhouse house is not to the left of the owner of the fish##8
14. the person who growsmarigold is the owner of the rat##1
15. the person who growsmarigold is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Flower         | amaryllis     | marigold   | bellflower | dahlia |
| House   | cottage | palace   | art-deco   | farmhouse  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Pet     | snake    | rat | bird     | fish    |

