.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, animation, thriller, drama
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, teacher, paramedic, accountant
4 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, go, domino
 1. the paramedic is between the person playing backgammon and the teacher##2
 2. the person watching animation movies is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
 3. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
 5. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the teacher##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
 7. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 8. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
 9. the fisherman is the person playing canasta##1
10. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
11. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the paramedic##8
12. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
13. the accountant is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the teacher is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
15. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the teacher##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
19. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Movie-Genre      | satire | thriller | drama  | animation  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Job   | teacher    | paramedic  | accountant | fisherman |
