4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, poker, domino
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, november, july, june
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
 3. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 4. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
 6. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 9. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
12. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Pet         | snake    | horse   | bird | hamster |
| Game   | canasta     | poker  | domino   | snooker      |
| Birthday   | november | september    | july      | june       |
