.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, plum
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, september, february, april
House: cottage, modern, wooden, colonial
4 different games are played: go, snooker, domino, bridge
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is not the cottage house##6
 2. the colonial house is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 3. the person eating plum is the wooden house##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the cottage house and the modern house##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 6. the person playing go is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the colonial house##1
10. the modern house is the person playing go##1
11. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
14. the modern house is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
15. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | cucumber    | banana             | apple   | plum     |
| Birthday   | may | february            | april | september    |
| House     | modern | colonial | cottage  | wooden |
| Game   | go  | snooker               | domino  | bridge   |

