.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, sunflower, rose
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lilac, mauve, purple
There are 4 different nationalities: british, malaysian, polish, russian
4 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, dog, ferret
 1. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8
 2. the russian is the person who growsdaisy##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person who growsamaryllis##6
 4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##8
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person who growsdaisy##8
 8. the malaysian is the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who growsrose##8
10. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
11. the owner of the ferret is between the person who growsrose and the person who likes lilac##2
12. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person who likes lilac##8
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Flower         | rose     | amaryllis | sunflower   | daisy  |
| Color   | purple | fuchsia   | lilac     | mauve  |
| Nationality   | british    | polish     | malaysian | russian  |
| Pet         | dog     | ferret | horse   | guinea-pig |

