The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, climbing, cricket
City: miami, liverpool, boston, berlin
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, singing, baking, gardening
 1. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the person traveling to berlin##6
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere between the person who's hobby is baking and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
11. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
12. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person traveling to miami##6
13. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
