 4. the social-worker is the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4
 6. the person who likes brown is somewhere between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to hannover##7
 7. the person who likes brown is not to the left of the person who likes ebony##8
 8. the person who likes blue is somewhere between the gothic-revival house and the modern house##7
 9. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
10. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8
11. the electrician is on the far left##1
12. the videographer is on the far right##1
13. the person who likes brown is the gothic-revival house##1
14. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the person traveling to hannover##8
15. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
16. the librarian is not to the left of the townhouse house##8

.:: Answer ::.
