 4. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
 5. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 7. the fan of jazz is between the fan of blues and the person driving the bus##2
