 9. the person playing chess is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
10. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
11. the person watching comedy movies is not to the left of the person playing snooker##8
12. the fan of punk is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
13. the person playing chess is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
