.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, russian, nigerian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, puzzles, filmmaking, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, disaster, drama, superhero
 1. the nigerian is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 3. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 4. the canadian is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the russian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 8. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the russian is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the japanese##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5

.:: Answer ::.
