 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 9. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
11. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
12. the nigerian is between the social-worker and the canadian##2
13. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

